    "When compared against commercial LLMs with much larger parameter counts (GPT-3.5, GPT-4, Med-PaLM, and Med-PaLM-2), MEDITRON-70B outperforms Med-PaLM and GPT-3.5 on all benchmarks, and achieves a higher score than GPT-4 on PubMedQA.",
